	(_bfd_coff_write_global_sym): Likewise.

	* cgc.c (copy_private_bfd_data): Always initialize the
	includes_phdrs field.

	* cgclink.h (cgc_fix_symbol_flags): Check for case where a non-CGC
	file defines a symbol first mentioned in an CGC file.

	* bfd-in.h: Always define BFD_HOST_64_BIT and BFD_HOST_U_64_BIT if
	possible, rather than only if BFD64.
